<i>Damn! What if you</i>
<i>wouldn't have gotten out of there?</i>

951
01:16:27,183 --> 01:16:29,083
Can you imagine
what he would--

952
01:16:37,727 --> 01:16:40,287
Katherine, we have
to call the police.

953
01:16:40,396 --> 01:16:42,990
We can't let her
just lie there.

954
